### Alle Tasks abrufen (Response mit listId)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tasks
Accept: application/json

###

### Einzelnen Task abrufen (Response mit listId)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tasks/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Neuen Task erstellen (Request-DTO: name, description, dueDate, completed, listId)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tasks
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Task-{{$timestamp}}",
  "description": "Beschreibung-{{$timestamp}}",
  "dueDate": "2025-12-31T00:00:00",
  "completed": false,
  "listId": 1
}

###

### Task teilweise aktualisieren
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "completed": false
}

